window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A bold English adventurer; an invincible Japanese warlord; a beautiful woman torn between two ways of life, two ways of love - all brought together in an extraordinary saga of a time and a place aflame with conflict, passion, ambition, lust, and the struggle for power. </p> <p>James Clavell's <i>Shōgun</i> is a modern classic, a masterpiece of historical fiction that will continue to endure for decades to come.</p>"; 
